verbs.description: homemake (third-person singular simple present homemakes, present participle homemaking, simple past and past participle homemade)

entries.meaning: (transitive) To prepare (a recipe, etc.) at home through one's own efforts, rather than buying it; to create homemade goods.

verbs.description: homemake (third-person singular simple present homemakes, present participle homemaking, simple past and past participle homemade)

entries.meaning: (intransitive) To manage a household; to engage in homemaking.
